OL,3,C'We're supposed to go on holiday in 6
OL,4,Cweeks': Killer dad in police custody
OL,5,Csuite
OL,7,FSimon Vickers can be heard discussing
OL,8,Fhis upcoming holiday to Gran Canaria
OL,9,Fin this CCTV footage released by the
OL,10,FCPS
OL,12,FKiller dad Simon Vickers appeared
OL,13,Fconcerned about his holiday plans
OL,14,Ffollowing the arrest for his
OL,15,Fdaughter's murder in the kitchen of
OL,16,Fthe family home.
OL,18,FIn CCTV footage from the custody
OL,19,Fsuite, Vickers was heard referencing
OL,20,Fthe family's plans to head off to Gran
OL,21,FCanaria in a matter of weeks.
