OL,3,C'We're supposed to go on holiday in 6
OL,4,Cweeks': Killer dad in police custody
OL,5,Csuite
OL,7,FHe had just been arrested over what he
OL,8,Fclaimed was a kitchen "play fight"
OL,9,Fwhich left his only daughter,
OL,10,FScarlett, with an 11cm stab wound from
OL,11,Fwhich she bled to death.
OL,13,FVideo captured by cameras in the
OL,14,Fpolice custody suite at Darlington
OL,15,Fpolice station captures Vickers
OL,16,Fsaying: "We're going on holiday to
OL,17,Ff***ing Gran Canaria in six weeks,
OL,18,Ff***ing hell man, I don't believe this
OL,19,Fis happening."
