OL,3,C'We're supposed to go on holiday in 6
OL,4,Cweeks': Killer dad in police custody
OL,5,Csuite
OL,7,FDuring his time in the custody suite,
OL,8,Fthe 50-year-old also explained the
OL,9,Fevents of the evening to officers.
OL,11,F"We were cooking tea, just mucking
OL,12,Fabout in the kitchen," he said. "I
OL,13,Fdon't understand how this is
OL,14,Fhappening, honestly."
OL,16,FAt his trial, he had insisted that his
OL,17,F14-year-old daughter's death was the
OL,18,Fresult of a "freak accident".
